# HangTheDJ v1
#
# This app requires NO environment variables and NO build step.
# All credentials are entered by the user in the browser UI and stored in
# localStorage — nothing is ever sent to a backend server.
#
# To run: serve this directory with any static HTTP server, e.g.:
#   python3 -m http.server 8080
#   npx serve .
#   # or deploy to GitHub Pages, Netlify, Vercel, Cloudflare Pages
#
# On first launch, the app will prompt you to enter:
#   1. Your Spotify Client ID (from https://developer.spotify.com/dashboard)
#   2. Your OpenAI API key (from https://platform.openai.com/api-keys)
#
# Set the Spotify Redirect URI to your app's URL, e.g.:
#   http://localhost:8080/
#   https://yourusername.github.io/hangthedj/
